1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. b4 Bxb4 5. c3 Ba5 6. d4 b5 7. Bd5 exd4 8. Qb3
Qf6 9. O-O h6 10. cxd4 Nge7 11. e5 Qf5 12. Nbd2 Nxd5 13. Qxd5 O-O 14. Ba3 b4
